This Bookmarklet [1] provides an easy way to create QR Codes [2] generated by Google Chart API [3].
It will prompt for an URL to be encoded.
The prompt will be pre populated with the URL of the current page.

[1] http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bookmarklet
[2] http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QR_Code
[3] http://code.google.com/apis/chart/
